<div class="header">
  <div class="header-content">
    <div class="tag">Original Research</div>
    <h1>Sandisk Corporation (SNDK)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Sandisk Corporation — using recent actuals, disclosed assumptions, and one final number.</p>
    <div class="compiler-tag">Compiled by Gemini 2.5 Pro</div>
    <p class="date">Updated March 18, 2026 · Data: StockAnalysis.com</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <!-- ═══ THE VERDICT ═══ -->
